{"tid":2229950,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中芯國際證實遭美國商務部制裁","createTime":"2020-10-04T16:40:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T18:10:57.000Z","uid":141151,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"017592096a57fb466575a1c06bb2c68c57f4166d","tid":2229950,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:40:40.000Z","msg":"中芯國際證實遭美國商務部制裁<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=407813\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D407813&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wilx9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=b4cf275a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D407813&h=55e23b48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=407813</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】中國最大晶片製造商中芯國際發出公告，證實受到美國商務部制裁，供應商要先申請出口許可證，才能夠向中芯國際供貨，公司指正與美國當局商討。<br />\n<br />\n中芯國際的公告證實，經過多日詢問供應商和討論後，公司知道美國商務部工業與安全局，根據美國出口管制條例，向部分供應商發信，對於向中芯國際出口的部分美國設備、配件和原物料，會受到美國出口管制規定的進一步限制，要事前申請出口許可證，才能夠向中芯國際繼續供貨。<br />\n<br />\n公司已經與美國當局初步交流，同時評估出口限制，對公司生產經營活動的影響。<br />\n<br />\n公告提醒，基於部分自美國出口的設備、配件和原材料供貨期會延長或有不準確性，公司未來的生產經營，可能會產生重要不利影響。<br />\n<br />\n中芯國際重申，一直堅持合規經營，遵守經營地的相關法律法規。<br />\n<br />\n英國傳媒上月引述美國商務部文件，指美方決定對中芯國際及其子公司、合資公司採取出口管制措施，據報中芯國際亦已經向各國上游供應商增加採購，為一旦遭美方制裁建立儲備。"},{"pid":"c8de27b363e39a5e3c1258ccbd54db36f1c9dc49","tid":2229950,"uid":86186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:41:19.000Z","msg":"恭喜晒"},{"pid":"9b48ec4b06626e6a4844b1c03502dc9c1cda4856","tid":2229950,"uid":66049,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:42:50.000Z","msg":"我真係恭喜你啊"},{"pid":"33f05a355bd5763b7817ee832fdce44093db6e87","tid":2229950,"uid":39796,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:43:22.000Z","msg":"春袋日日俾人揸住<br />\n無撚用既"},{"pid":"2293398eaefe1de242c067e000a0e5d91112e034","tid":2229950,"uid":127929,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:44:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uMXWOhL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuMXWOhL.gif&h=35cb550b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1738989e8546c85c64d29ad73ef20fbbfd2baf59","tid":2229950,"uid":46275,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:44:40.000Z","msg":"內循環，未撚驚過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96510a02db987011f0f413da435d278305429e2e","tid":2229950,"uid":258381,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:46:03.000Z","msg":"可以專注自煮燃發<br />\n終國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日爆升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf2f324322f2fa0929c380cf770f1b0c34849915","tid":2229950,"uid":13663,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:47:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e99Vjqh.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe99Vjqh.gif&h=8f66d0c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c8ae7485495379846498a2a0bdf862916f92d43","tid":2229950,"uid":271807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:47:04.000Z","msg":"實在太興奮"},{"pid":"347d706abe9a5e6420395c11988bd17462f66757","tid":2229950,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:50:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b973c264f707a210aabb32ed286b621cd1aee445","tid":2229950,"uid":66378,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:51:16.000Z","msg":"許多在中國國內的人才都支持中芯，美國的決定打破了不少人的幻想，不是壞事（not bad），而且如今支持中芯的中國人對美國芯片的興趣也大大降低。"},{"pid":"75bb3430efb11a4163aaad4ca5c5f039f4061d32","tid":2229950,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T17:02:43.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji